originalText.text: Dee was such a pleasure to work with.  It's the first time in my life I was actually happy to pay a broker because she worked her butt off for it.  We saw 2 dozen apartments in my desired neighborhood.  She would meet me whenever, wherever and even weekends to walk apartments.  She doesn't waste time, listens to your suggestions and is thoughtful with what is important to the renter.  Wear comfortable shoes though because she walks fast! :)

originalText.text: Dee is a very good broker and a very nice and friendly person. She was extremely helpful in finding us an apartment which could fit all our needs and demands (and they were more than a few :) ). With great patience and always a big smile she found the best solution in terms of place and price to accommodate us. Strongly recommended!!

originalText.text: Dee is a very professional, patient, friendly broker. She will gives you what are you looking for. Just tell her your requirements, she will help you to find a perfect apartment that meets all your requirements. Many other agents just keep pushing you to decide,but Dee won't. Also she will tell you the real estate market knowledge, I learnt a lot from her. Very nice person , when I have mind to moving, I'll consider her again.

originalText.text:
I first met Dee a year ago when I wanted to buy an apt in Brooklyn Heights. Not only did she find me the perfect apt that's well within my budget, she also negotiated relentlessly to broker the deal. I couldn't be happier as a client and as a friend!

Later on when I needed to rent the apt out she came through for me again.

If you need a broker that you can trust and rely on, Dee is the one!

originalText.text: Dee was fantastic. She was punctual, knowledgeable, professional and had a great sense of what was out there. Most importantly, she wasn't at all pushy. She was patient and wanted to be sure we found something we loved and were excited about. She ended up finding us a hidden gem in one of the nicest neighborhoods down town---a deal almost too good to be true. We will definitely be using Dee again in the future!
